---
const reviews = [
  {
    name: "Arjun Mehta",
    role: "Marketing Specialist",
    content:
      "My stage fright was so severe that I'd stay silent in every meeting. Upraizo’s Public Speaking module completely rewired my confidence. I’m no longer just attending meetings—I’m leading them. The shift from hesitation to influence has been the biggest turning point in my career this year.",
    initials: "AM",
  },
  {
    name: "Priya Sharma",
    role: "Freelance Designer",
    content:
      "Handling difficult clients and negotiating rates used to drain me. The negotiation frameworks here taught me how to communicate my value without sounding aggressive. My client conversion rate has jumped by 40%, and I've finally stopped undercharging for my work.",
    initials: "PS",
  },
  {
    name: "Rohan Khanna",
    role: "Engineering Team Lead",
    content:
      "Moving from a dev role to a lead position showed me that technical skills aren't enough. Upraizo’s modules on Emotional Intelligence and conflict resolution helped me bridge the communication gap with my team. We’re more aligned now, and project delivery is smoother than ever.",
    initials: "RK",
  },
  {
    name: "Ishita Verma",
    role: "MBA Graduate",
    content:
      "During placements, I struggled to articulate my story effectively. The 'Art of Storytelling' course taught me how to structure my experiences into a compelling narrative. It gave me the edge I needed to land a role at a top-tier MNC. This is the stuff they don't teach you in grad school.",
    initials: "IV",
  },
  {
    name: "Sandeep Nair",
    role: "Sales Director",
    content:
      "Confidence isn't just a feeling; it's a skill. From body language to voice modulation, the attention to detail in these courses is incredible. It has made my sales pitches 10x more persuasive. If you're in a high-stakes environment, these soft skills are your secret weapon.",
    initials: "SN",
  },
  {
    name: "Anjali Gupta",
    role: "Product Manager",
    content:
      "Critical thinking and managing stakeholder expectations are the hardest parts of my job. Upraizo provided me with logical frameworks to stay calm and decisive under pressure. It’s practical, no-nonsense learning that actually sticks. Every modern professional needs this toolkit.",
    initials: "AG",
  },
];
---

<section
  id="reviews"
  class="py-24 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 cursor-default"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2
        class="text-xs font-black text-red-600 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4"
      >
        Testimonials
      </h2>
      <h3
        class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
      >
        Real Stories, Real Growth
      </h3>
      <p
        class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-medium leading-relaxed"
      >
        See how our students are mastering communication, building unshakable confidence, and accelerating their careers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      {
        reviews.map((review) => (
          <div class="relative p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-zinc-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800/80 transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-zinc-200/50 dark:hover:shadow-black/50 hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-zinc-200/60 dark:bg-zinc-800/50 blur-[60px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-100 opacity-70" />

            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
              <div class="mb-6 text-zinc-300 dark:text-zinc-700">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="40"
                  height="40"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                >
                  <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
                </svg>
              </div>

              <p class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 font-medium leading-relaxed text-lg mb-10">
                "{review.content}"
              </p>

              <div class="mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/40 dark:bg-zinc-950/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/50 dark:border-zinc-800/50 shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-bold text-lg tracking-wide">
                  {review.initials}
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-0.5">
                    {review.name}
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 font-medium">
                    {review.role}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>